{"id":5600,"date":"2025-07-26T17:26:47","date_gmt":"2025-07-26T14:26:47","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/aminidigital.co.ke\/?page_id=5600"},"modified":"2025-07-26T18:23:42","modified_gmt":"2025-07-26T15:23:42","slug":"remarketing-ad-campaign-services-in-kenya","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/aminidigital.co.ke\/services\/remarketing-ad-campaign-services-in-kenya\/","title":{"rendered":"Remarketing Ad Campaign Services in Kenya"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; type=&#8221;vc_default&#8221; margin_top=&#8221;5&#8243; margin_bottom=&#8221;10&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1716548610536{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column]<div id=\"ultimate-heading-1339695ec17adb752\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-1339695ec17adb752 uvc-4064 \" data-hspacer=\"no_spacer\"  data-halign=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><div class=\"uvc-heading-spacer no_spacer\" style=\"top\"><\/div><div class=\"uvc-main-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-1339695ec17adb752 h2'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"desktop:44px;\",\"line-height\":\"desktop:54px;\"}' ><h2 style=\"font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:45px;\">Remarketing Ad Campaign Services in Kenya \u2013 Reconnect and Convert Lost Visitors<\/h2><\/div><\/div>[vc_single_image image=&#8221;5602&#8243; img_size=&#8221;full&#8221; alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; lazy_loading=&#8221;true&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"83\" data-end=\"130\">What Is Remarketing and Why Is It Essential?<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"132\" data-end=\"427\">Remarketing, also referred to as retargeting, is a digital advertising strategy that allows you to serve targeted ads to users who previously interacted with your website or mobile app but did not complete a desired action\u2014such as making a purchase, submitting a form, or downloading a resource.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"429\" data-end=\"644\">It\u2019s not just a buzzword. It\u2019s a fundamental part of any high-performing digital strategy\u2014especially in Kenya, where the online consumer journey is fragmented across multiple devices, platforms, and decision points.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"662\">How It Works<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"664\" data-end=\"870\">Remarketing Ad Campaign Services in Kenya rely on tracking technologies\u2014such as cookies, Facebook Pixel, Google Ads tags, and CRM-based audience lists\u2014to identify visitors and follow them with relevant ads across the web. For example:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"872\" data-end=\"1188\">\n<li data-start=\"872\" data-end=\"974\">\n<p data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"974\">A visitor browses your e-commerce store, adds a product to the cart but leaves without checking out.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"975\" data-end=\"1104\">\n<p data-start=\"977\" data-end=\"1104\">That user then sees a dynamic product ad on Facebook or a YouTube bumper ad reminding them of the exact product they abandoned.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1105\" data-end=\"1188\">\n<p data-start=\"1107\" data-end=\"1188\">With the right timing, creative, and offer, they return to complete the purchase.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1190\" data-end=\"1366\">This follow-up is what sets remarketing apart from traditional advertising\u2014it reaches people who are already <em data-start=\"1299\" data-end=\"1306\">aware<\/em> of your brand and <em data-start=\"1325\" data-end=\"1333\">likely<\/em> to convert with the right nudge.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1368\" data-end=\"1407\">Why Remarketing Is Critical in 2025<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1409\" data-end=\"1694\">According to research by Think with Google, over 90% of consumers in emerging markets, including Kenya, switch between devices and platforms during their buying journey. That means the first visit is almost never the last. If you don\u2019t continue the conversation, someone else will.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1696\" data-end=\"1708\">Furthermore:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"2121\">\n<li data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"1864\">\n<p data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1864\">97% of website visitors don\u2019t convert on their first visit \u2013 especially in high-consideration industries like insurance, education, or B2B services.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1865\" data-end=\"2002\">\n<p data-start=\"1867\" data-end=\"2002\">Retargeted ads can boost conversion rates by up to 150% compared to display ads shown to cold audiences (Source: WordStream, 2024).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2003\" data-end=\"2121\">\n<p data-start=\"2005\" data-end=\"2121\">CTR (click-through rate) for remarketing ads is 10x higher than that of standard display ads (Retargeter, 2024).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2123\" data-end=\"2182\">With such numbers, it\u2019s no longer optional. It\u2019s necessary.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2184\" data-end=\"2202\">Where It Works<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2204\" data-end=\"2258\">Remarketing can be implemented across major platforms:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2259\" data-end=\"2555\">\n<li data-start=\"2259\" data-end=\"2330\">\n<p data-start=\"2261\" data-end=\"2330\">Google Display Network \u2013 ads across millions of websites and apps<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2331\" data-end=\"2409\">\n<p data-start=\"2333\" data-end=\"2409\">Facebook and Instagram \u2013 social feeds, Stories, and Messenger placements<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2410\" data-end=\"2467\">\n<p data-start=\"2412\" data-end=\"2467\">YouTube \u2013 skippable and non-skippable in-stream ads<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2468\" data-end=\"2555\">\n<p data-start=\"2470\" data-end=\"2555\">TikTok, X (Twitter), LinkedIn \u2013 niche targeting and campaign-specific retargeting<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2557\" data-end=\"2744\">It also pairs seamlessly with CRMs like HubSpot, Salesforce, or email platforms, allowing businesses to segment and re-engage lapsed leads based on behavioural data\u2014not just demographics.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2746\" data-end=\"2762\">Key Benefits<\/h3>\n<ol data-start=\"2764\" data-end=\"3214\">\n<li data-start=\"2764\" data-end=\"2848\">\n<p data-start=\"2767\" data-end=\"2848\">Second Chances to Convert \u2013 Target visitors who showed intent but didn\u2019t act.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2849\" data-end=\"2921\">\n<p data-start=\"2852\" data-end=\"2921\">Higher ROI \u2013 You\u2019re spending on warm leads, not cold impressions.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2922\" data-end=\"3029\">\n<p data-start=\"2925\" data-end=\"3029\">Better Personalisation \u2013 Tailor ad messages based on user behaviour (e.g. specific products viewed).<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3030\" data-end=\"3111\">\n<p data-start=\"3033\" data-end=\"3111\">Brand Recall \u2013 Keep your business top-of-mind through consistent exposure.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3112\" data-end=\"3214\">\n<p data-start=\"3115\" data-end=\"3214\">Scalable Across Funnels \u2013 Whether it\u2019s awareness or reactivation, remarketing fits every stage.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h3 data-start=\"3216\" data-end=\"3263\">Kenyan Context: Why It Matters More Locally<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3265\" data-end=\"3592\">In Kenya, many online shoppers are cautious\u2014whether due to payment security concerns, product trust, or budget constraints. They research, compare, and delay decision-making. Retargeting allows businesses to maintain visibility during this delay, helping to build trust and increase conversions when the buyer is finally ready.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3594\" data-end=\"3793\">For NGOs and service-based companies, remarketing also serves as a reminder mechanism\u2014nudging users to complete forms, download reports, or register for programmes they previously showed interest in.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"46\">Why You\u2019re Losing Sales Without Remarketing<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"48\" data-end=\"295\">Every day, Kenyan businesses spend thousands of shillings to bring users to their websites\u2014through SEO, Google Ads, Meta ads, or influencer marketing. But here\u2019s the uncomfortable truth: most of that traffic doesn\u2019t convert on the first visit.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"297\" data-end=\"436\">Remarketing solves that problem. Without it, you&#8217;re effectively letting most of your marketing budget leak out with nothing to show for it.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"438\" data-end=\"494\">1. 97% of Users Don\u2019t Convert on the First Visit<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"496\" data-end=\"755\">According to Forrester Research and reaffirmed in HubSpot\u2019s 2024 eCommerce Benchmarks, approximately 97% of visitors leave without taking any meaningful action. That includes purchasing a product, submitting a lead form, or downloading a resource.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"757\" data-end=\"1011\">In Kenya, consumer behaviour is no different. For e-commerce, buyers compare prices on Jumia, Instagram shops, WhatsApp sellers, and independent stores before making a final choice. For service businesses, leads often delay action for days or even weeks.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1013\" data-end=\"1086\">Without a way to continue the conversation, that initial click is wasted.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1088\" data-end=\"1144\">2. Kenyan Consumers Comparison-Shop Aggressively<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1146\" data-end=\"1172\">Most Kenyan consumers now:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1173\" data-end=\"1421\">\n<li data-start=\"1173\" data-end=\"1230\">\n<p data-start=\"1175\" data-end=\"1230\">Check multiple sellers before deciding who to trust<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1231\" data-end=\"1322\">\n<p data-start=\"1233\" data-end=\"1322\">Pause to confirm payment security, delivery times, or genuine product reviews<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1323\" data-end=\"1421\">\n<p data-start=\"1325\" data-end=\"1421\">Use mobile-first platforms like WhatsApp, TikTok, and Facebook Marketplace to compare offers<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1423\" data-end=\"1643\">Remarketing ad campaign services in Kenya allows you to re-engage these consumers with tailored messaging\u2014reminding them of the specific product or service they viewed, or sweetening the deal with a time-limited offer, free delivery, or social proof.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1645\" data-end=\"1728\">Without this, they\u2019re likely to forget you and choose a more persistent competitor.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1730\" data-end=\"1778\">3. You&#8217;re Relying on Cold Audiences Only<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1780\" data-end=\"1809\">Let\u2019s break this down simply.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1811\" data-end=\"2119\">If your digital ad budget is 100% focused on reaching new people (cold traffic), and 0% on people who <em data-start=\"1913\" data-end=\"1927\">already know<\/em> your brand, you&#8217;re playing an inefficient game. Cold traffic takes time and repetition to convert. Warm traffic\u2014those who\u2019ve visited your site\u2014are cheaper to re-engage and more likely to act.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2121\" data-end=\"2161\">A Meta ad study in 2023 showed that:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2162\" data-end=\"2365\">\n<li data-start=\"2162\" data-end=\"2215\">\n<p data-start=\"2164\" data-end=\"2215\">Cold audiences needed 6\u20138 ad impressions to convert<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2216\" data-end=\"2285\">\n<p data-start=\"2218\" data-end=\"2285\">Warm (remarketing) audiences often converted after just 2\u20133 touches<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2286\" data-end=\"2365\">\n<p data-start=\"2288\" data-end=\"2365\">Cost per acquisition (CPA) dropped by up to 60% when remarketing was used<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2367\" data-end=\"2418\">4. You\u2019re Missing the Chance to Build Trust<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2420\" data-end=\"2620\">In high-consideration industries like financial services, education, B2B tech, or healthcare, users often need reassurance before committing. Remarketing enables that trust-building phase by offering:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2621\" data-end=\"2734\">\n<li data-start=\"2621\" data-end=\"2635\">\n<p data-start=\"2623\" data-end=\"2635\">Testimonials<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2636\" data-end=\"2654\">\n<p data-start=\"2638\" data-end=\"2654\">Product benefits<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2655\" data-end=\"2705\">\n<p data-start=\"2657\" data-end=\"2705\">Educational content (blog links, videos, guides)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2706\" data-end=\"2734\">\n<p data-start=\"2708\" data-end=\"2734\">Brand messaging and values<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2736\" data-end=\"2833\">Without these soft follow-ups, your audience forgets you, even if they initially showed interest.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2835\" data-end=\"2896\">5. Reacquisition Costs Are Higher Without Remarketing<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2898\" data-end=\"2917\">Let\u2019s do the maths.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2919\" data-end=\"3153\">If you\u2019re paying Ksh 15 per click to drive traffic, and 95 out of 100 people bounce, that\u2019s Ksh 1,425 of your budget wasted unless you retarget them. The cost of reacquiring those same users via another cold campaign could double.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3155\" data-end=\"3304\">With a remarketing funnel in place, the same users can be re-engaged for Ksh 2\u20135 per impression or less, depending on the platform and audience size.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3306\" data-end=\"3422\">That\u2019s not just more efficient\u2014it\u2019s essential for profitability in today\u2019s competitive Kenyan digital landscape.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221;][vc_column][vc_cta h2=&#8221;Need to Rank in Featured Snippets?&#8221; h2_font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000&#8243; h2_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; h2_css_animation=&#8221;fadeInLeft&#8221; h4_font_container=&#8221;tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%230A0A0A&#8221; h4_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; shape=&#8221;square&#8221; style=&#8221;flat&#8221; color=&#8221;grey&#8221; add_button=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_title=&#8221;Contact Us&#8221; btn_shape=&#8221;square&#8221; btn_color=&#8221;warning&#8221; btn_i_align=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_i_icon_fontawesome=&#8221;fa fa-solid fa-paper-plane&#8221; btn_css_animation=&#8221;bounceIn&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h2=&#8221;true&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h4=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_add_icon=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_link=&#8221;url:%23!%2Fcontact&#8221;]Request an Answer Engine audit to find out if your content qualifies for Google\u2019s instant answers.[\/vc_cta][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"52\">What Our Remarketing Ad Campaign Services Include<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"54\" data-end=\"372\">At amini Digital Agency, we don\u2019t run generic ad campaigns. We design full-funnel remarketing systems that reconnect your brand with high-intent audiences, based on actual user behaviour. Our approach is not about chasing everyone\u2014it\u2019s about pursuing the <em data-start=\"307\" data-end=\"314\">right<\/em> people with the <em data-start=\"331\" data-end=\"338\">right<\/em> message, on the <em data-start=\"355\" data-end=\"362\">right<\/em> platform.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"374\" data-end=\"580\">Whether you\u2019re running an e-commerce business, an NGO campaign, or a B2B lead gen funnel, our remarketing services are engineered to recover missed opportunities and maximise your return on ad spend (ROAS).<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"582\" data-end=\"607\">Audience Segmentation<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"609\" data-end=\"777\">Effective remarketing begins with <strong data-start=\"643\" data-end=\"666\">precision targeting<\/strong>. We help you build granular audience segments based on how people interact with your site, CRM, or mobile app.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"779\" data-end=\"826\">We create custom remarketing audiences such as:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"828\" data-end=\"1573\">\n<li data-start=\"828\" data-end=\"983\">\n<p data-start=\"830\" data-end=\"983\"><strong data-start=\"830\" data-end=\"869\">Website visitors who didn\u2019t convert<\/strong><br data-start=\"869\" data-end=\"872\" \/>Includes homepage viewers, product page viewers, or people who visited a service page but didn\u2019t take action.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"985\" data-end=\"1170\">\n<p data-start=\"987\" data-end=\"1170\"><strong data-start=\"987\" data-end=\"1006\">Cart abandoners<\/strong><br data-start=\"1006\" data-end=\"1009\" \/>Especially powerful for Shopify, WooCommerce, and Magento stores. We show the exact product the user left behind, with urgency or discounts to nudge them back.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1377\">\n<p data-start=\"1174\" data-end=\"1377\"><strong data-start=\"1174\" data-end=\"1196\">Unresponsive leads<\/strong><br data-start=\"1196\" data-end=\"1199\" \/>Visitors who downloaded a brochure, requested a quote, or submitted a contact form but never followed through. We re-engage them with reminder offers, testimonials, or content.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1379\" data-end=\"1573\">\n<p data-start=\"1381\" data-end=\"1573\"><strong data-start=\"1381\" data-end=\"1399\">Past customers<\/strong><br data-start=\"1399\" data-end=\"1402\" \/>Ideal for upselling, cross-selling, or requesting product reviews. E.g., if someone bought school textbooks, they can be retargeted with learning resources or workbooks.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1575\" data-end=\"1678\">We also help you exclude recent converters so that your ads don\u2019t waste budget on already closed deals.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1680\" data-end=\"1707\">Ad Creative Development<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1709\" data-end=\"1867\">In remarketing, <strong data-start=\"1725\" data-end=\"1743\">relevance wins<\/strong>. Showing the same generic ad to everyone doesn\u2019t work. Our creative strategy ensures your ads feel timely and personalised.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1869\" data-end=\"1880\">We develop:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1881\" data-end=\"2591\">\n<li data-start=\"1881\" data-end=\"2074\">\n<p data-start=\"1883\" data-end=\"2074\"><strong data-start=\"1883\" data-end=\"1906\">Dynamic product ads<\/strong><br data-start=\"1906\" data-end=\"1909\" \/>Automatically show users the exact products they viewed or added to cart. This works seamlessly with Shopify, WooCommerce, and Google Merchant Center integrations.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2076\" data-end=\"2238\">\n<p data-start=\"2078\" data-end=\"2238\"><strong data-start=\"2078\" data-end=\"2112\">Custom visuals by funnel stage<\/strong><br data-start=\"2112\" data-end=\"2115\" \/>We use softer, educational messaging for top-of-funnel audiences and harder CTAs or urgency-based messages for hot leads.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2240\" data-end=\"2433\">\n<p data-start=\"2242\" data-end=\"2283\"><strong data-start=\"2242\" data-end=\"2268\">Multi-format creatives<\/strong><br data-start=\"2268\" data-end=\"2271\" \/>Including:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2286\" data-end=\"2433\">\n<li data-start=\"2286\" data-end=\"2307\">\n<p data-start=\"2288\" data-end=\"2307\">Image ads (JPG\/PNG)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2310\" data-end=\"2321\">\n<p data-start=\"2312\" data-end=\"2321\">Carousels<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2324\" data-end=\"2347\">\n<p data-start=\"2326\" data-end=\"2347\">Short videos and GIFs<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2350\" data-end=\"2379\">\n<p data-start=\"2352\" data-end=\"2379\">Explainers and testimonials<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2382\" data-end=\"2433\">\n<p data-start=\"2384\" data-end=\"2433\">Story-format creatives for Instagram and Facebook<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2435\" data-end=\"2591\">\n<p data-start=\"2437\" data-end=\"2591\"><strong data-start=\"2437\" data-end=\"2467\">Platform-optimised content<\/strong><br data-start=\"2467\" data-end=\"2470\" \/>Our team adapts designs for each placement\u2014whether a Facebook feed, YouTube pre-roll, TikTok, or Google Display banner.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2593\" data-end=\"2668\">We refresh ad creatives regularly to avoid ad fatigue and banner blindness.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2670\" data-end=\"2701\">Platform Setup and Tracking<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2703\" data-end=\"2875\">No campaign is effective without <strong data-start=\"2736\" data-end=\"2771\">proper tracking and attribution<\/strong>. Our team sets up and configures all the essential tags and events to ensure every action is monitored.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2877\" data-end=\"2890\">We implement:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2891\" data-end=\"3382\">\n<li data-start=\"2891\" data-end=\"2951\">\n<p data-start=\"2893\" data-end=\"2951\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/business\/tools\/meta-pixel\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong data-start=\"2893\" data-end=\"2911\">Facebook Pixel<\/strong><\/a> for Meta (Facebook\/Instagram) campaigns<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2952\" data-end=\"2985\">\n<p data-start=\"2954\" data-end=\"2985\"><strong data-start=\"2954\" data-end=\"2985\">Google Ads remarketing tags<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2986\" data-end=\"3074\">\n<p data-start=\"2988\" data-end=\"3074\"><strong data-start=\"2988\" data-end=\"3016\">Google Analytics 4 (GA4)<\/strong> for custom audience creation and event-based segmentation<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3075\" data-end=\"3153\">\n<p data-start=\"3077\" data-end=\"3153\"><strong data-start=\"3077\" data-end=\"3102\">Custom event tracking<\/strong> for downloads, video views, form submissions, etc.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3154\" data-end=\"3288\">\n<p data-start=\"3156\" data-end=\"3288\"><strong data-start=\"3156\" data-end=\"3176\">CRM integrations<\/strong> with platforms like HubSpot, Salesforce, Mailchimp, and Zoho to build remarketing audiences from lead behaviour<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3289\" data-end=\"3382\">\n<p data-start=\"3291\" data-end=\"3382\"><strong data-start=\"3291\" data-end=\"3321\">Consent-compliant tracking<\/strong> aligned with GDPR and Kenya Data Protection Act requirements<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3384\" data-end=\"3460\">All setups are double-checked to ensure clean data and reliable conversions.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"3462\" data-end=\"3500\">Campaign Management &amp; Optimisation<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3502\" data-end=\"3677\">Once your campaigns are live, our work doesn\u2019t stop there. We treat remarketing as a <strong data-start=\"3587\" data-end=\"3615\">living, breathing system<\/strong> that must adapt to performance trends and audience behaviour.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3679\" data-end=\"3713\">Our optimisation process includes:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3715\" data-end=\"4159\">\n<li data-start=\"3715\" data-end=\"3805\">\n<p data-start=\"3717\" data-end=\"3805\"><strong data-start=\"3717\" data-end=\"3734\">Split testing<\/strong> (A\/B testing) of headlines, creatives, placements, and calls to action<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3806\" data-end=\"3851\">\n<p data-start=\"3808\" data-end=\"3851\"><strong data-start=\"3808\" data-end=\"3829\">Frequency capping<\/strong> to avoid user burnout<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3852\" data-end=\"3912\">\n<p data-start=\"3854\" data-end=\"3912\"><strong data-start=\"3854\" data-end=\"3875\">Budget allocation<\/strong> based on campaign ROI, not guesswork<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3913\" data-end=\"4002\">\n<p data-start=\"3915\" data-end=\"4002\"><strong data-start=\"3915\" data-end=\"3934\">Funnel analysis<\/strong> to understand which messages drive action and where drop-offs occur<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"4003\" data-end=\"4074\">\n<p data-start=\"4005\" data-end=\"4074\"><strong data-start=\"4005\" data-end=\"4039\">Weekly creative refresh cycles<\/strong> to keep content fresh and relevant<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"4075\" data-end=\"4159\">\n<p data-start=\"4077\" data-end=\"4159\"><strong data-start=\"4077\" data-end=\"4098\">Monthly reporting<\/strong> with ROAS, CPC, conversion rates, and attribution breakdowns<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"4161\" data-end=\"4278\">We constantly review results and iterate until your remarketing campaign becomes one of your top-performing channels.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"37\">Remarketing Platforms We Work With<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"39\" data-end=\"312\">Effective remarketing requires selecting the right platform for your audience and campaign goals. At amini Digital Agency, we don\u2019t take a one-size-fits-all approach\u2014we recommend channels based on where your users actually spend their time and how they engage across devices.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"314\" data-end=\"418\">Below is a breakdown of the main remarketing platforms we use and how they apply to businesses in Kenya:<\/p>\n<div class=\"_tableContainer_80l1q_1\">\n<div class=\"_tableWrapper_80l1q_14 group flex w-fit flex-col-reverse\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<table class=\"w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)\" data-start=\"420\" data-end=\"1474\">\n<thead data-start=\"420\" data-end=\"550\">\n<tr data-start=\"420\" data-end=\"550\">\n<th data-start=\"420\" data-end=\"441\" data-col-size=\"sm\"><strong data-start=\"422\" data-end=\"434\">Platform<\/strong><\/th>\n<th data-start=\"441\" data-end=\"493\" data-col-size=\"md\"><strong data-start=\"443\" data-end=\"455\">Use Case<\/strong><\/th>\n<th data-start=\"493\" data-end=\"550\" data-col-size=\"md\"><strong data-start=\"495\" data-end=\"509\">Ad Formats<\/strong><\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody data-start=\"683\" data-end=\"1474\">\n<tr data-start=\"683\" data-end=\"814\">\n<td data-start=\"683\" data-end=\"704\" data-col-size=\"sm\"><strong data-start=\"685\" data-end=\"703\">Google Display<\/strong><\/td>\n<td data-start=\"704\" data-end=\"756\" data-col-size=\"md\">Reach users across websites, blogs, and apps<\/td>\n<td data-start=\"756\" data-end=\"814\" data-col-size=\"md\">Static banners, responsive display, animated GIFs<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr data-start=\"815\" data-end=\"946\">\n<td data-start=\"815\" data-end=\"836\" data-col-size=\"sm\"><strong data-start=\"817\" data-end=\"828\">YouTube<\/strong><\/td>\n<td data-start=\"836\" data-end=\"888\" data-col-size=\"md\">Target video viewers or past website visitors<\/td>\n<td data-start=\"888\" data-end=\"946\" data-col-size=\"md\">Skippable and non-skippable in-stream, bumper ads<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr data-start=\"947\" data-end=\"1078\">\n<td data-start=\"947\" data-end=\"968\" data-col-size=\"sm\"><strong data-start=\"949\" data-end=\"961\">Facebook<\/strong><\/td>\n<td data-start=\"968\" data-end=\"1020\" data-col-size=\"md\">Social media remarketing for desktop and mobile<\/td>\n<td data-start=\"1020\" data-end=\"1078\" data-col-size=\"md\">Carousels, single image, video, Instant Experience<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr data-start=\"1079\" data-end=\"1210\">\n<td data-start=\"1079\" data-end=\"1100\" data-col-size=\"sm\"><strong data-start=\"1081\" data-end=\"1094\">Instagram<\/strong><\/td>\n<td data-start=\"1100\" data-end=\"1152\" data-col-size=\"md\">Mobile-first remarketing for lifestyle or product<\/td>\n<td data-start=\"1152\" data-end=\"1210\" data-col-size=\"md\">Reels, Stories, Explore placements, carousels<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr data-start=\"1211\" data-end=\"1342\">\n<td data-st