forming.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1900\" data-end=\"1923\">YouTube Retargeting<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1925\" data-end=\"1972\">We use <a href=\"https:\/\/aminidigital.co.ke\/services\/youtube-ads-services-in-kenya\/\">YouTube<\/a> to serve video ads to users who:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1973\" data-end=\"2075\">\n<li data-start=\"1973\" data-end=\"1992\">\n<p data-start=\"1975\" data-end=\"1992\">Visited your site<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1993\" data-end=\"2027\">\n<p data-start=\"1995\" data-end=\"2027\">Watched part of a previous video<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2028\" data-end=\"2075\">\n<p data-start=\"2030\" data-end=\"2075\">Subscribed to your channel but didn\u2019t convert<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2077\" data-end=\"2201\">For example, a non-profit can run a 15-second bumper ad targeting users who landed on their donation page but didn\u2019t donate.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2203\" data-end=\"2234\">Meta (Facebook &amp; Instagram)<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2236\" data-end=\"2341\"><a href=\"https:\/\/aminidigital.co.ke\/services\/facebook-instagram-advertising-services-in-kenya\/\">Facebook and Instagram<\/a> offer deep remarketing options using the Meta Pixel and Custom Audiences. You can:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2342\" data-end=\"2535\">\n<li data-start=\"2342\" data-end=\"2400\">\n<p data-start=\"2344\" data-end=\"2400\">Show carousel ads with the exact products a user browsed<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2401\" data-end=\"2465\">\n<p data-start=\"2403\" data-end=\"2465\">Run testimonial videos to people who visited your pricing page<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2466\" data-end=\"2535\">\n<p data-start=\"2468\" data-end=\"2535\">Serve vertical creatives in Stories for higher visibility on mobile<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2537\" data-end=\"2648\">We run separate creatives for Facebook feeds vs. Instagram Stories to ensure proper formatting and performance.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2650\" data-end=\"2672\">TikTok Remarketing<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2674\" data-end=\"2764\"><a href=\"https:\/\/aminidigital.co.ke\/services\/tiktok-advertising-services-in-kenya\/\">TikTok<\/a> is growing fast in Kenya, especially among younger consumers. We retarget based on:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2765\" data-end=\"2860\">\n<li data-start=\"2765\" data-end=\"2783\">\n<p data-start=\"2767\" data-end=\"2783\">Video engagement<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2784\" data-end=\"2800\">\n<p data-start=\"2786\" data-end=\"2800\">Website visits<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2801\" data-end=\"2860\">\n<p data-start=\"2803\" data-end=\"2860\">Add-to-cart events (when e-commerce platforms support it)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2862\" data-end=\"2958\">It\u2019s effective for short, mobile-first retargeting in industries like fashion, FMCG, and events.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2960\" data-end=\"2975\">X (Twitter)<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2977\" data-end=\"3084\">Although niche, <a href=\"https:\/\/aminidigital.co.ke\/services\/x-formerly-twitter-advertising-services-in-kenya\/\">X<\/a> can support remarketing tied to trending topics, news, or live events. It works well for:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3085\" data-end=\"3164\">\n<li data-start=\"3085\" data-end=\"3111\">\n<p data-start=\"3087\" data-end=\"3111\">Conferences and webinars<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3112\" data-end=\"3129\">\n<p data-start=\"3114\" data-end=\"3129\">Media campaigns<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3130\" data-end=\"3164\">\n<p data-start=\"3132\" data-end=\"3164\">Political or advocacy-based NGOs<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3166\" data-end=\"3284\">We use Twitter&#8217;s audience manager to create retargeting pools based on site visits or engagement with promoted tweets.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221;][vc_column][vc_cta h2=&#8221;Want to appear in featured snippets and voice search?&#8221; h2_font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000&#8243; h2_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; h2_css_animation=&#8221;fadeInLeft&#8221; h4_font_container=&#8221;tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%230A0A0A&#8221; h4_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; shape=&#8221;square&#8221; style=&#8221;flat&#8221; color=&#8221;grey&#8221; add_button=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_title=&#8221;Contact Us&#8221; btn_shape=&#8221;square&#8221; btn_color=&#8221;warning&#8221; btn_i_align=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_i_icon_fontawesome=&#8221;fa fa-solid fa-paper-plane&#8221; btn_css_animation=&#8221;bounceIn&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h2=&#8221;true&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h4=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_add_icon=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_link=&#8221;url:%23!%2Fcontact&#8221;]Let\u2019s optimise your content for Google\u2019s answer features. Talk to us today.[\/vc_cta][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"49\">Who Should Run a Remarketing Ad Campaign Services in Kenya<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"51\" data-end=\"257\">Remarketing isn\u2019t just for large corporations with massive ad budgets. It\u2019s for any Kenyan business, organisation, or institution that drives traffic to a website or app but isn\u2019t seeing enough conversions.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"259\" data-end=\"433\">If your marketing efforts bring people to your digital platforms\u2014but they leave without taking action\u2014you\u2019re the right candidate for remarketing. Below are specific examples.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"435\" data-end=\"484\">1. <strong data-start=\"442\" data-end=\"484\">E-commerce Stores With Abandoned Carts<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"486\" data-end=\"753\">Online retailers are often hit hardest by abandonment. In Kenya, cart abandonment rates range between <strong data-start=\"588\" data-end=\"598\">65\u201380%<\/strong>, depending on the industry. Users browse, add items to their cart, and then drop off\u2014sometimes due to delivery concerns, payment options, or distractions.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"755\" data-end=\"1015\"><strong data-start=\"755\" data-end=\"768\">Use case:<\/strong><br data-start=\"768\" data-end=\"771\" \/>An online furniture store sees thousands of visitors a week. Only 5% check out. With remarketing, the store can display dynamic ads showing the specific products each user abandoned\u2014alongside offers like free delivery or limited-time discounts.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1017\" data-end=\"1052\">2. <strong data-start=\"1024\" data-end=\"1052\">Lead Generation Websites<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1054\" data-end=\"1218\">If your business relies on capturing leads via contact forms, quote requests, or content downloads, you\u2019re likely losing many potential clients without remarketing.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1220\" data-end=\"1471\"><strong data-start=\"1220\" data-end=\"1233\">Use case:<\/strong><br data-start=\"1233\" data-end=\"1236\" \/>A law firm runs Google Ads to drive traffic to a legal services page. Only 10% of visitors fill out the form. Remarketing allows the firm to re-engage the other 90% with trust-building ads that answer FAQs or share client testimonials.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1473\" data-end=\"1522\">3. <strong data-start=\"1480\" data-end=\"1522\">NGOs and Non-Profits Running Campaigns<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1524\" data-end=\"1679\">Non-profits often spend on awareness campaigns that bring users to landing pages for donations, sign-ups, or downloads\u2014but many users leave without acting.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1681\" data-end=\"1947\"><strong data-start=\"1681\" data-end=\"1694\">Use case:<\/strong><br data-start=\"1694\" data-end=\"1697\" \/>An education-focused NGO runs a digital literacy campaign. Visitors read the impact stories but don\u2019t sign up or donate. A remarketing sequence can re-engage these users with a short video, a call to action, or success stories that reinforce urgency.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1949\" data-end=\"2009\">4. <strong data-start=\"1956\" data-end=\"2009\">SaaS and B2B Businesses With Long Decision Cycles<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2011\" data-end=\"2261\">For software products, consulting firms, or B2B solutions, decisions are rarely made in one visit. Visitors explore, download a brochure, attend a webinar, and only then reach out. Remarketing is key to staying visible during that evaluation process.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2263\" data-end=\"2494\"><strong data-start=\"2263\" data-end=\"2276\">Use case:<\/strong><br data-start=\"2276\" data-end=\"2279\" \/>A local CRM provider gets demo requests but loses leads before conversion. We run remarketing ads with pricing information, feature overviews, or customer success stories to nurture these leads back into the funnel.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2496\" data-end=\"2552\">5. <strong data-start=\"2503\" data-end=\"2552\">Any Business With Traffic But Low Conversions<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2554\" data-end=\"2639\">Even if your business doesn&#8217;t fit neatly into one of the above categories, if you\u2019re:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2640\" data-end=\"2794\">\n<li data-start=\"2640\" data-end=\"2685\">\n<p data-start=\"2642\" data-end=\"2685\">Getting traffic from social media or Google<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2686\" data-end=\"2737\">\n<p data-start=\"2688\" data-end=\"2737\">Not seeing proportional sales, sign-ups, or calls<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2738\" data-end=\"2794\">\n<p data-start=\"2740\" data-end=\"2794\">Not following up with that traffic in a structured way<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2796\" data-end=\"2861\">\u2026then remarketing should be a core part of your digital strategy.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"35\">Our Remarketing Campaign Process<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"37\" data-end=\"250\">amini Digital Agency follows a structured, data-led process to build and manage remarketing ad campaign services in Kenya that perform. Our goal is simple: help you convert more of your existing traffic at a lower cost per acquisition.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"252\" data-end=\"405\">We combine audience data, behavioural signals, platform expertise, and creative testing into a repeatable framework that ensures results\u2014not assumptions.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"407\" data-end=\"427\">Here\u2019s how we do it:<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"429\" data-end=\"466\">1. Define Clear Remarketing Goals<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"468\" data-end=\"628\">We start by identifying what success looks like. Is it recovering abandoned carts? Increasing form submissions? Re-engaging past leads? Generating repeat sales?<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"630\" data-end=\"656\">Examples of typical goals:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"657\" data-end=\"856\">\n<li data-start=\"657\" data-end=\"709\">\n<p data-start=\"659\" data-end=\"709\">Boost checkout completion rate for an online store<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"757\">\n<p data-start=\"712\" data-end=\"757\">Increase return visits to a key campaign page<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"758\" data-end=\"805\">\n<p data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"805\">Convert past form fillers into paying clients<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"806\" data-end=\"856\">\n<p data-start=\"808\" data-end=\"856\">Move stalled leads through a longer sales funnel<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"858\" data-end=\"1012\">We match these goals with the right remarketing approach\u2014awareness, consideration, or conversion\u2014and select the right platform and ad formats accordingly.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1014\" data-end=\"1069\">2. Segment Audiences Using Behavioural and CRM Data<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1071\" data-end=\"1182\">Next, we map out your remarketing audiences. We don\u2019t treat all visitors the same. We categorise them based on:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1183\" data-end=\"1304\">\n<li data-start=\"1183\" data-end=\"1198\">\n<p data-start=\"1185\" data-end=\"1198\">Pages visited<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1199\" data-end=\"1216\">\n<p data-start=\"1201\" data-end=\"1216\">Products viewed<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1217\" data-end=\"1237\">\n<p data-start=\"1219\" data-end=\"1237\">Time spent on site<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1238\" data-end=\"1275\">\n<p data-start=\"1240\" data-end=\"1275\">Interaction with forms or downloads<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1276\" data-end=\"1304\">\n<p data-start=\"1278\" data-end=\"1304\">Email opens and CRM status<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1306\" data-end=\"1335\">We integrate with tools like:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1336\" data-end=\"1484\">\n<li data-start=\"1336\" data-end=\"1362\">\n<p data-start=\"1338\" data-end=\"1362\">Google Analytics 4 (GA4)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1363\" data-end=\"1390\">\n<p data-start=\"1365\" data-end=\"1390\">Facebook Custom Audiences<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1391\" data-end=\"1413\">\n<p data-start=\"1393\" data-end=\"1413\">LinkedIn Insight Tag<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1414\" data-end=\"1450\">\n<p data-start=\"1416\" data-end=\"1450\">Email tools (e.g. Mailchimp, Zoho)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1451\" data-end=\"1484\">\n<p data-start=\"1453\" data-end=\"1484\">CRMs (e.g. Salesforce, HubSpot)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1486\" data-end=\"1628\">These segments are grouped by intent level\u2014so we serve different ads to someone who viewed your homepage vs. someone who abandoned a checkout.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1630\" data-end=\"1669\">3. Design Personalised Ad Creatives<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1671\" data-end=\"1757\">With audience intent in mind, we develop ad creatives that are specific to each group.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1759\" data-end=\"2006\">\n<li data-start=\"1759\" data-end=\"1824\">\n<p data-start=\"1761\" data-end=\"1824\">For cart abandoners: Product-focused ads with urgency or offers<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1825\" data-end=\"1898\">\n<p data-start=\"1827\" data-end=\"1898\">For previous content downloaders: Testimonials, benefits, or next steps<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1899\" data-end=\"1956\">\n<p data-start=\"1901\" data-end=\"1956\">For past customers: Upsells, reviews, or loyalty offers<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1957\" data-end=\"2006\">\n<p data-start=\"1959\" data-end=\"2006\">For cold leads: Video explainers or brand proof<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2008\" data-end=\"2196\">Creatives are designed in multiple formats and optimised for each platform\u2019s technical specs\u2014whether that\u2019s a Facebook carousel, a Google responsive display ad, or a TikTok vertical video.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2198\" data-end=\"2265\">We create a full creative matrix to avoid overexposure and fatigue.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2267\" data-end=\"2314\">4. Launch Campaigns Across Chosen Platforms<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2316\" data-end=\"2375\">We configure campaign settings across platforms, including:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2376\" data-end=\"2552\">\n<li data-start=\"2376\" data-end=\"2396\">\n<p data-start=\"2378\" data-end=\"2396\">Audience targeting<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2397\" data-end=\"2416\">\n<p data-start=\"2399\" data-end=\"2416\">Budget allocation<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2417\" data-end=\"2433\">\n<p data-start=\"2419\" data-end=\"2433\">Frequency caps<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2434\" data-end=\"2510\">\n<p data-start=\"2436\" data-end=\"2510\">Geographic targeting (e.g. Nairobi only, Kenya-wide, or diaspora-specific)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2511\" data-end=\"2552\">\n<p data-start=\"2513\" data-end=\"2552\">Device types and time-of-day scheduling<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2554\" data-end=\"2654\">This stage includes linking your ad accounts to our reporting dashboards for real-time transparency.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2656\" data-end=\"2776\">We then launch test campaigns first, allowing us to benchmark performance and gather early signals before scaling spend.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2778\" data-end=\"2822\">5. Monitor, Optimise, and Refresh Weekly<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2824\" data-end=\"2876\">Once campaigns go live, our performance team tracks:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2877\" data-end=\"3014\">\n<li data-start=\"2877\" data-end=\"2903\">\n<p data-start=\"2879\" data-end=\"2903\">Click-through rate (CTR)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2904\" data-end=\"2927\">\n<p data-start=\"2906\" data-end=\"2927\">Conversion rate (CVR)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2928\" data-end=\"2956\">\n<p data-start=\"2930\" data-end=\"2956\">Cost per acquisition (CPA)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2957\" data-end=\"2984\">\n<p data-start=\"2959\" data-end=\"2984\">Return on ad spend (ROAS)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2985\" data-end=\"3014\">\n<p data-start=\"2987\" data-end=\"3014\">Frequency and reach metrics<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3016\" data-end=\"3043\">We run A\/B tests to refine:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3044\" data-end=\"3096\">\n<li data-start=\"3044\" data-end=\"3053\">\n<p data-start=\"3046\" data-end=\"3053\">Ad copy<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3054\" data-end=\"3063\">\n<p data-start=\"3056\" data-end=\"3063\">Visuals<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3064\" data-end=\"3083\">\n<p data-start=\"3066\" data-end=\"3083\">Audience segments<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3084\" data-end=\"3096\">\n<p data-start=\"3086\" data-end=\"3096\">Placements<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3098\" data-end=\"3274\">If a creative or segment underperforms, we replace or refine it fast. Weekly optimisations are non-negotiable. This is how we turn decent campaigns into high-performing assets.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"3276\" data-end=\"3318\">6. Report Conversions and ROAS Monthly<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3320\" data-end=\"3389\">At the end of every month, you receive a structured report detailing:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"3390\" data-end=\"3530\">\n<li data-start=\"3390\" data-end=\"3409\">\n<p data-start=\"3392\" data-end=\"3409\">Spend per channel<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3410\" data-end=\"3435\">\n<p data-start=\"3412\" data-end=\"3435\">Conversions per segment<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3436\" data-end=\"3474\">\n<p data-start=\"3438\" data-end=\"3474\">Revenue generated (where applicable)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3475\" data-end=\"3493\">\n<p data-start=\"3477\" data-end=\"3493\">ROAS by platform<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"3494\" data-end=\"3530\">\n<p data-start=\"3496\" data-end=\"3530\">Recommendations for the next cycle<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"3532\" data-end=\"3654\">This helps your team make informed decisions about scaling budgets, shifting platforms, or adjusting the broader strategy.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221;][vc_column][vc_cta h2=&#8221;Want to optimise your site for AEO?&#8221; h2_font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000&#8243; h2_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; h2_css_animation=&#8221;fadeInLeft&#8221; h4_font_container=&#8221;tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%230A0A0A&#8221; h4_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; shape=&#8221;square&#8221; style=&#8221;flat&#8221; color=&#8221;grey&#8221; add_button=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_title=&#8221;Contact Us&#8221; btn_shape=&#8221;square&#8221; btn_color=&#8221;warning&#8221; btn_i_align=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_i_icon_fontawesome=&#8221;fa fa-solid fa-paper-plane&#8221; btn_css_animation=&#8221;bounceIn&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h2=&#8221;true&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h4=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_add_icon=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_link=&#8221;url:%23!%2Fcontact&#8221;]Work With Kenya\u2019s AEO Experts[\/vc_cta][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"52\">Why Choose amini Digital Agency for Retarg