nd funnel architecture<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2581\" data-end=\"2648\">\n<p data-start=\"2583\" data-end=\"2648\"><strong data-start=\"2583\" data-end=\"2614\">Designers and video editors<\/strong> with platform-specific experience<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2649\" data-end=\"2715\">\n<p data-start=\"2651\" data-end=\"2715\"><strong data-start=\"2651\" data-end=\"2671\">Tracking experts<\/strong> who configure pixels, events, and analytics<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2716\" data-end=\"2786\">\n<p data-start=\"2718\" data-end=\"2786\"><strong data-start=\"2718\" data-end=\"2738\">Account managers<\/strong> who report with clarity and take responsibility<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2788\" data-end=\"2853\">This vertical integration ensures accountability and performance.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221;][vc_column][vc_cta h2=&#8221;Need to improve your rankings?&#8221; h2_font_container=&#8221;tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000&#8243; h2_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; h2_css_animation=&#8221;fadeInLeft&#8221; h4_font_container=&#8221;tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%230A0A0A&#8221; h4_use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; shape=&#8221;square&#8221; style=&#8221;flat&#8221; color=&#8221;grey&#8221; add_button=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_title=&#8221;Contact Us&#8221; btn_shape=&#8221;square&#8221; btn_color=&#8221;warning&#8221; btn_i_align=&#8221;right&#8221; btn_i_icon_fontawesome=&#8221;fa fa-solid fa-paper-plane&#8221; btn_css_animation=&#8221;bounceIn&#8221; css=&#8221;&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h2=&#8221;true&#8221; use_custom_fonts_h4=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_add_icon=&#8221;true&#8221; btn_link=&#8221;url:%23!%2Fcontact&#8221;]Our results speak for themselves. Contact us today.[\/vc_cta][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"45\">Case Studies \u2013 Retargeting That Drives ROI<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"47\" data-end=\"306\">We believe in showing results\u2014not vague promises. Below are real examples of how amini Digital Agency has helped businesses and organisations in Kenya recover lost revenue and improve return on ad spend (ROAS) through focused, data-driven remarketing campaigns.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"308\" data-end=\"365\">Fashion E-commerce: 52% Cart Recovery Rate in 30 Days<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"367\" data-end=\"510\"><strong data-start=\"367\" data-end=\"378\">Client:<\/strong> Mid-sized online fashion retailer based in Nairobi<br data-start=\"429\" data-end=\"432\" \/><strong data-start=\"432\" data-end=\"444\">Problem:<\/strong> Over 75% of customers were abandoning their carts<br data-start=\"494\" data-end=\"497\" \/><strong data-start=\"497\" data-end=\"510\">Solution:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"511\" data-end=\"708\">\n<li data-start=\"511\" data-end=\"565\">\n<p data-start=\"513\" data-end=\"565\">Set up dynamic product ads on Facebook and Instagram<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"566\" data-end=\"635\">\n<p data-start=\"568\" data-end=\"635\">Created urgency-based creatives (e.g. \u201cStill thinking about this?\u201d)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"636\" data-end=\"708\">\n<p data-start=\"638\" data-end=\"708\">Split audiences by time since abandonment (e.g. 1\u20133 days vs. 4\u20137 days)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"739\"><strong data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"739\">Results (within 30 days):<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"740\" data-end=\"828\">\n<li data-start=\"740\" data-end=\"764\">\n<p data-start=\"742\" data-end=\"764\">52% cart recovery rate<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"765\" data-end=\"776\">\n<p data-start=\"767\" data-end=\"776\">5.4x ROAS<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"777\" data-end=\"828\">\n<p data-start=\"779\" data-end=\"828\">32% reduction in CPA compared to cold traffic ads<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"830\" data-end=\"915\">This client scaled the campaign by 2.5x in month two after seeing consistent results.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1717845133697{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221; bg_color_value=&#8221;#f4f4f4&#8243; el_id=&#8221;!\/contact&#8221;][vc_column]<div id=\"ultimate-heading-8672695ec17adbb4e\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-8672695ec17adbb4e uvc-1167  uvc-heading-default-font-sizes\" data-hspacer=\"line_with_icon\" data-hline_width=\"100\" data-hicon_type=\"selector\" data-hborder_style=\"solid\" data-hborder_height=\"5\" data-hborder_color=\"#3697ca\" data-icon_width=\"32\" data-hfixer=\"5\"  data-halign=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><div class=\"uvc-main-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-8672695ec17adbb4e h2'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}' ><h2 style=\"--font-weight:theme;\">Get in touch and let's discuss your Digital Marketing needs<\/h2><\/div><div class=\"uvc-heading-spacer line_with_icon\" style=\"topheight:32px;\"><div class=\"ult-just-icon-wrapper  \"><div class=\"align-icon\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<div class=\"aio-icon none \"  style=\"color:#3697ca;font-size:32px;display:inline-block;\">\n\t<i class=\"fas fa-angle-down\"><\/i>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"uvc-sub-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-8672695ec17adbb4e .uvc-sub-heading '  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}'  style=\"font-weight:normal;margin-bottom:20px;\">Get a Tailored Solution &amp; Free Quote<\/div><\/div>[vc_row_inner equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_column_inner width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1717584696266{background-image: url(https:\/\/aminidigital.co.ke\/wp-content\/uploads