questions we get from businesses and organisations exploring remarketing in Kenya.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div>[vc_tta_accordion][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Is remarketing expensive?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715360052221-d2dccac3-2f8e82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"244\" data-end=\"563\">No. In fact, remarketing is usually more cost-effective than standard ad campaigns. Since you&#8217;re targeting users who already know your brand, cost-per-click (CPC) and cost-per-conversion (CPA) tend to be lower. Most clients see a higher return on ad spend (ROAS) with remarketing compared to cold traffic campaigns.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"565\" data-end=\"699\"><strong data-start=\"565\" data-end=\"577\">Example:<\/strong><br data-start=\"577\" data-end=\"580\" \/>Where a cold campaign might cost Ksh 100\u2013150 per lead, a remarketing campaign might convert the same lead at Ksh 40\u201370.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;How do you track users across platforms?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715360052312-795bf34f-889a82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"751\" data-end=\"778\">We use tracking tools like:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"779\" data-end=\"926\">\n<li data-start=\"779\" data-end=\"824\">\n<p data-start=\"781\" data-end=\"824\">Meta Pixel (for Facebook and Instagram)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"825\" data-end=\"857\">\n<p data-start=\"827\" data-end=\"857\">Google Ads Remarketing Tag<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"858\" data-end=\"888\">\n<p data-start=\"860\" data-end=\"888\">Google Analytics 4 (GA4)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"889\" data-end=\"926\">\n<p data-start=\"891\" data-end=\"926\">CRM and email list integrations<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"928\" data-end=\"1181\">These tools let us build audiences based on website actions (e.g. viewed a product, started a form) or CRM behaviour (e.g. opened a sales email but didn\u2019t convert). All tracking is set up in compliance with Kenyan and international data protection laws.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Is remarketing only for e-commerce?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361191995-ff8a0d69-1fe982d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1228\" data-end=\"1254\">No. Remarketing works for:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1255\" data-end=\"1406\">\n<li data-start=\"1255\" data-end=\"1285\">\n<p data-start=\"1257\" data-end=\"1285\">Lead generation websites<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1286\" data-end=\"1316\">\n<p data-start=\"1288\" data-end=\"1316\">Service-based businesses<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1317\" data-end=\"1334\">\n<p data-start=\"1319\" data-end=\"1334\">Non-profits<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1335\" data-end=\"1360\">\n<p data-start=\"1337\" data-end=\"1360\">Education providers<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1361\" data-end=\"1381\">\n<p data-start=\"1363\" data-end=\"1381\">SaaS companies<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1382\" data-end=\"1406\">\n<p data-start=\"1384\" data-end=\"1406\">Government portals<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1408\" data-end=\"1535\">Any organisation with digital traffic and a conversion goal\u2014sign-ups, calls, downloads, purchases\u2014can benefit from remarketing.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;What kind of creative works best?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361240947-6ed290f2-a03582d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1580\" data-end=\"1709\">Creative depends on the audience segment and funnel stage. That said, the best performing remarketing creatives in Kenya include:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"1908\">\n<li data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"1750\">\n<p data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1750\"><strong data-start=\"1712\" data-end=\"1735\">Dynamic product ads<\/strong> for e-commerce<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1751\" data-end=\"1796\">\n<p data-start=\"1753\" data-end=\"1796\"><strong data-start=\"1753\" data-end=\"1773\">Explainer videos<\/strong> for service businesses<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1797\" data-end=\"1846\">\n<p data-start=\"1799\" data-end=\"1846\"><strong data-start=\"1799\" data-end=\"1822\">Client testimonials<\/strong> or case studies for B2B<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1847\" data-end=\"1908\">\n<p data-start=\"1849\" data-end=\"1908\"><strong data-start=\"1849\" data-end=\"1883\">Short, mobile-optimised videos<\/strong> for TikTok and Instagram<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1910\" data-end=\"2049\">We test creatives weekly to improve relevance and performance. What works in month one may not work in month three\u2014so we adapt continually.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=&#8221;Can you run remarketing even if we didn\u2019t work with you before?&#8221; tab_id=&#8221;1715361291476-30b845c7-304f82d6-a9a5&#8243;][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"2124\" data-end=\"2251\">Yes. We can take over or audit existing Google, Meta, or YouTube ad accounts and plug in remarketing layers. We\u2019ll review your:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2252\" data-end=\"2366\">\n<li data-start=\"2252\" data-end=\"2278\">\n<p data-start=\"2254\" data-end=\"2278\">Website or landing pages<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2279\" data-end=\"2317\">\n<p data-start=\"2281\" data-end=\"2317\">Existing ad pixels or tracking setup<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2318\" data-end=\"2348\">\n<p data-start=\"2320\" data-end=\"2348\">CRM or email marketing flows<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2349\" data-end=\"2366\">\n<p data-start=\"2351\" data-end=\"2366\">Creative assets<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2368\" data-end=\"2462\">From there, we build out targeted remarketing campaigns without disrupting your current setup.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_tta_section][\/vc_tta_accordion][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<